<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
  <title>DOP Fix complete — {{batchLabel}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont,
        'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #F4F4F5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    .card {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .header {
      background: #0A0A0A;
      padding: 24px 32px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .header p {
      color: #A1A1AA;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin: 4px 0 0;
    }
    .body {
      padding: 28px 32px;
    }
    .lede {
      color: #3F3F46;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      margin: 0 0 20px;
    }
    .summary {
      background: #F4F4F5;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      margin: 0 0 20px;
    }
    .summary .row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #18181B;
      padding: 6px 0;
    }
    .summary .row + .row {
      border-top: 1px solid #E4E4E7;
    }
    .summary .row.headline {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .summary .row .label {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .summary .row .value {
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .bucket {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .bucket .bucket-title {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: #71717A;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .bucket .examples {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #3F3F46;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .review-list {
      background: #FFF7ED;
      border: 1px solid #FED7AA;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      margin: 16px 0 0;
    }
    .review-list .bucket-title {
      color: #C2410C;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .review-list .examples {
      color: #9A3412;
    }
    .btn {
      display: block;
      padding: 12px;
      background: #0A0A0A;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 24px 0 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 18px 32px;
      border-top: 1px solid #E4E4E7;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #A1A1AA;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>DOP Fix complete</h1>
      <p>{{batchLabel}} · {{environment}} · batch {{batchId}}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p class="lede">
        The Fix cascade just finished for this batch. Hours, rating,
        cover and taxonomy were applied where mappable. Anything below
        the "Needs review" line still needs operator attention.
      </p>
      <div class="summary">
        <div class="row headline">
          <span class="label">✅ Fully fixed</span>
          <span class="value">{{fullyFixed}} / {{total}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="label">🕒 Hours written</span>
          <span class="value">{{countsHours}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="label">⭐ Rating captured</span>
          <span class="value">{{countsRating}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="label">🖼 Cover synced</span>
          <span class="value">{{countsCover}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <span class="label">🏷 Taxonomy corrected</span>
          <span class="value">{{countsTaxonomy}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{examplesHtml}}

      {{reviewHtml}}

      <a href="{{resolveUrl}}" class="btn">
        Open Resolve →
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      Batch {{batchId}} · {{completedAtLabel}} · sent by PinnTag DOP
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
